  "title": "Staff Nurse [5 Days | Office Hours | Buangkok] - 2323",
  "description": "<p><strong>Staff Nurse</strong></p><ul><li>Salary range : $2500 - $4,000</li><li>Location : Buangkok</li><li>Working Days:  5 days / week </li><li>Monday - Sunday 8am to 6pm / 8am -5pm</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out preventive and curative medical services under the guidance of the doctor and head nurse</li><li>Oversee the general health of the residents: participate in and supervise medical and nursing care routine</li><li>Supervise and assess the performance of nursing aides and health attendants</li><li>Assist and carry out emergency situations in the Home</li><li>The Staff Nurse will report to the Head Nursing and Therapy</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least a diploma / degree / professional degree in Nursing</li><li>Candidate must be a State Registered Nurse with valid certificate by the Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</li></ul><p><strong>To expedite the process interested candidates may contact me with your resume via:</strong></p><p><strong>Whatsapp: +65 8012 4526(Alvin)</strong></p><p><strong>Alvin Chua Ming Jing | R23116192</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | 14C7279</strong></p><p><br /></p>",
